      • closeEntry

        void closeEntry()
        Deprecated. 
        This function is called when the flag entry popup is closed on data commit. It closes any open flag entry with an unflagged date.

      • setFieldsOnResolution

        void setFieldsOnResolution()
        Deprecated. 
        This function is called when a FlagEntry's resolution field is set. This function sets the UnflagDate and UnflagUser fields. This serves the role of a "FlagEntry Pre-Update" rule set.
